<li>I am so incredibly sorry to hear about the loss of your friend.  My heart goes out to you.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and sending all my love during this painful time.</li>
<li>I'm here for you, whatever you need.  Don't hesitate to reach out.</li>
<li>I was so saddened to hear about [deceased's name]. They will be deeply missed.</li>
<li>Your friendship with [deceased's name] was truly special. I'll always cherish the memories of them.</li>
<li> Sending you strength and comfort as you grieve.</li>
<li>Remembering [deceased's name] with fondness and sending you my deepest sympathy.</li>
<li>I'm so sorry for your loss.  May you find peace and solace.</li>
<li> Holding you close in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
